''']\n|[[Limassol]]\n|178,5m\n|585,5ft\n|43\n|2023\n|Approved\n|Residential\n|<small>To be erected at a plot where a shopping mall currently stands<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://auralimassol.com/|title=Aura Limassol|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref></small>\n|-\n|-\n|-\n|-\n|- style=\"background:#FFB347;\"\n|2\n|[https://www.burohappold.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/one-limassol_00b_circ-create-HBA.jpg '''One''']\n|[[Limassol]]\n|170m\n|558ft\n|38\n|2020\n|Under Construction\n|Residential\n|<small>Upon completion 'One' will be [[Cyprus]]' tallest tower and Europe's tallest seafront residential building. 'One' has topped out at 153m and awaits its 17m metal arch<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.onelimassol.com/en/home|title=ONE {{!}} Iconic Address - Limassol|website=www.onelimassol.com|access-date=2020-01-28}}</ref></small>\n|- style=\"background:#FFB347;\"\n|3\n|[https://trilogylimassol.com/storage/app/media/homepage/2.Towers-home-page1670x1150.jpg '''Trilogy'''] <small>West Tower (1/3)</small>\n|[[Limassol]]\n| 161m\n|528ft\n| 39\n|2021\n|Under Construction\n|Residential\n|<small>Concrete foundations poured. Now climbing above ground level<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://trilogylimassol.com/|title=Trilogy Limassol Seafront: Your Story Begins Here {{!}} Live - Work - Play|website=trilogylimassol.com|access-date=2020-01-28}}</ref></small>\n|- style=\"background:#FFB347;\"\n|4\n|'''[https://www.pafilia.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/neo-hero-1920x900.jpg Limassol NEO]''' <small>'''Riva''' (1/4)</small>\n|[[Limassol]]\n|\u2248160m\n|\u2248525ft\n|39\n|2022\n|Under Construction\n|Residential\n|<small>Construction of concrete foundation<ref name=\":1\">{{Cite web|url=http://neolimassol.com/|title=Neo \u2013 Between The Sky And The Sea|language=en-US|access-date=2020-01-28}}</ref></small>\n|-\n|-\n|- style=\"background: pink;\"\n|5\n|[https://www.papachristou.org/wp-content/uploads/Radisson_Final-View_6_JPEG_FT.