oads/2019/02/neo-hero-1920x900.jpg Limassol NEO]''' <small>'''Una''' (4/4)</small>\n|[[Limassol]]\n|\u2248100m\n|\u2248328ft\n|25\n|2025\n|Approved\n|Residential\n|<small>On hold: Construction expected to begin in 2021<ref name=\":1\" /></small>\n|-\n|- style=\"background:#FFB347;\"\n|29\n|[https://www.uha.london/uploads/projects/Infinity_Towers/1222/Infinity_Tower_view_1B_1980.jpg '''Infinity Towers'''] <small>(1/2)</small>\n|[[Limassol]]\n|100m\n|328ft\n|25\n|2022\n|Broke Ground\n|Residential\n|<small>Groundworks stage<ref name=\":10\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.prime-property.com/en/Development/Infinity_Towers/|title=Infinity Towers|website=PRIME PROPERTY|language=en|access-date=2020-01-28}}</ref></small>\n|-\n|- style=\"background:#FFB347;\"\n|30\n|[https://www.uha.london/uploads/projects/Infinity_Towers/1222/Infinity_Tower_view_1B_1980.jpg '''Infinity Towers'''] <small>(2/2)</small>\n|[[Limassol]]\n|100m\n|328ft\n|25\n|2022\n|Broke Ground\n|Residential\n|<small>Groundworks stage<ref name=\":10\" /></small>\n|- style=\"background: pink;\"\n|31\n|[http://renewable.gr//wp-content/uploads/2017/10/16-LORD-BYRON-CYPRUS_up-1024x597.jpg '''Lord Byron''']\n|[[Nicosia]]\n|100m\n|328ft\n|17\n|\n|Proposed\n|Commercial\n|<small>Considered to be a stale proposal<ref name=\":5\" /></small>\n|- style=\"background:#FFB347;\"\n|32\n|[http://pericleous.com.cy/storage/app/media/projects/sky_1.jpg '''Sky Tower''']\n|[[Limassol]]\n|98m\n|321,5ft\n|23\n|2021\n|Under Construction\n|Residential\n|<small>Feb 2020 - The 'Sky Tower' has almost topped out<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.prime-property.com/en/Development/Sky_Tower/|title=Sky Tower {{!}} Prime Property Group|website=PRIME PROPERTY|language=en|access-date=2020-01-28}}</ref></small>\n|-\n|- style=\"background:#87CEFA;\"\n|33\n|[http://oxleyplanetvision.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/01.jpg '''Sofitel Residences'''] <small>(2/2)</small>\n|[[Limassol]]\n|97m\n|318ft\n|20\n|2022\n|Approved\n|Residential\n|<small>Two residential to