curring}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Valerie Cruz]]\n| Joy Mendez\n| {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Timoth\u00e9e Chalamet]]\n| [[#Finn Walden|Finn Walden]]\n| {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Talia Balsam]]\n| [[#Cynthia Walden|Cynthia Walden]]\n| {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Tim Guinee]]\n| Scott Ryan\n| {{cNone}}\n| {{cGuest|Guest}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n|-\n| [[Mido Hamada]]\n| M.M.\n| {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Chance Kelly]]\n| Mitchell Clawson\n| {{cNone}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Sam Underwood]]\n| Leo Carras\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| Gary Wilmes\n| Troy Richardson\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Jason Butler Harner]]\n| [[#Paul Franklin|Paul Franklin]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Shaun Toub]]\n| [[#Majid Javadi|Majid Javadi]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[William Abadie]]\n| [[#Alan Bernard|Alan Bernard]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[William Sadler (actor)|William Sadler]]\n| [[#Michael Higgins|Michael Higgins]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Suraj Sharma]]\n| Aayan Ibrahim\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Alex Lanipekun]]\n| Hank Wonham\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| Akshay Kumar\n| Rahim\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| Shavani Seth\n| Kiran\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| Claire Keane<br />McKenna Keane</small>{{efn|In the fourth season, Franny is portrayed by an uncredited baby actress. In the fifth season, Franny is portrayed by baby actresses Luna and Lotta Pfitzer.}}\n| Frances Mathison\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Michael O'Keefe]]\n| John Redmond\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Mark Moses]]\n| Dennis Boyd\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Raza Jaffrey]]\n| Aasar Khan\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Art Malik]]\n| Bunran Latif\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n|-\n| [[Nina Hoss]]\n| Astrid\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[John Getz]]\n| Joe Crocker\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| Atheer Adel\n| Numan\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| Sven Schelker\n| Armand Korzenik\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Micah Hauptman]]\n| Mills\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Allan Corduner]]\n| Etai Luskin\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cNone}}\n|-\n| [[Mark Ivanir]]\n| Ivan Krupin\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cNone}}\n| {{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{cNone}}\n| {{cGuest|Guest}}\n| {{cNone}}\n|-\n| Alireza Bayram\n| Qasim\n| colspan=\"4\"